<ul><li>The atoms of the sample are&nbsp;<b>ionised</b>&nbsp;and directed in a narrow beam at&nbsp;<b>at the same velocity</b>&nbsp;into a&nbsp;<b>uniform magnetic field</b>.</li><li>Each ion is deflected in a semi-circle by the magnetic field onto the detector.</li><li>The radius of curvature of the path of each ion&nbsp;<b>depends on the specific charge</b>&nbsp;of the ion.</li></ul>